data.eml:eml: New Prionospio and Laubieriellus (Annelida: Spionidae) species from Southeastern Brazil

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Peixoto, Antônio João Malafaia, Paiva, Paulo Cesar De (2019): New Prionospio and Laubieriellus (Annelida: Spionidae) species from Southeastern Brazil. Zootaxa 4577 (3): 529-547, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4577.3.7
